Date: Fri, 15 Dec 95 15:46:00 PST
From: "Finger, Jeanne L." <FingerJL@bv.com>
Return-Path: FingerJL@bv.com
Subject: XP-SWMM File
To: Bob Dickinson at XP Software <xpsoft@shadow.net>


Per our conversation today, I have attached the XP-SWMM file, 5MC.XP for 
your review.  There are 822 nodes and 824 links.  The file is > 1.7 Mbytes, 
and there are approximately 16,381 lines.  The file appeared to be OK up to 
today, when during my editing session, data would suddenly "disappear" from 
the nodes and conduits.  When I get back from vacation, I will look into 
installing Version 2 and trying out my file using it.
Thanks for offering to look at this file.
Have a Happy Christmas and/or Hannukah and New Year's Eve,
Jeanne Finger

